{
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "verse_number": 1,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:1",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "عَبَسَ وَتَوَلَّىٰٓ",
      "translation": "眉をひそめて、背を向けた、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "verse_number": 2,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:2",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَن جَآءَهُ ٱلۡأَعۡمَىٰ",
      "translation": "自分のもとに、盲目の者が来たために。[1]",
      "footnotes": "[1]　アッ＝ラーズィー* によれば、解釈学者らは、このアーヤ*が預言者*ムハンマド*と教友*イブン・ウンム・マクトゥームに関して下ったということで、一致している（11：５３参照）。預言者*はある時、クライシュ族*の有力者らがムスリム*になることを望み、彼らをイスラーム*へと熱心に招いていた。そのような場にやって来た盲目のイブン・ウンム・マクトゥーム*の教えを彼にしつこくせがんでしまう。預言者*は話を邪魔されるのを嫌い、彼を相手にせず、有力者たちへの話に勤しんだ。このアーヤ*が下ってそのことを咎められた後、預言者*は彼を大事に扱い、重用するようになった（アル＝バガウィー５：21０参照）。尚、預言者*・使徒*の無謬（むびゅう）性については、雌牛章３６の訳注を参照。"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "verse_number": 3,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:3",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَمَا يُدۡرِيكَ لَعَلَّهُۥ يَزَّكَّىٰٓ",
      "translation": "そして、何があなたに（彼の真実を）知らせるのか？彼が清められる[1]かもしれない、ということを？",
      "footnotes": "[1]　ここでの「清められる」とは、預言者*からの教えを得ることで、自らの宗教においてより清浄となり、無知という闇が消えさること、とされる（アル＝クルトゥビー1９：21３参照）。"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "verse_number": 4,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:4",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَوۡ يَذَّكَّرُ فَتَنفَعَهُ ٱلذِّكۡرَىٰٓ",
      "translation": "あるいは、彼が教訓を受け、それで教訓が彼を益するかもしれないことを？",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "verse_number": 5,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:5",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَمَّا مَنِ ٱسۡتَغۡنَىٰ",
      "translation": "（導きなしでも）十分だとする者[1]はといえば、",
      "footnotes": "[1]　これは善への意欲がないため、質問も教示も請うこともないようなもののこと（アッ＝サアディー９1０頁参照）。"
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "verse_number": 6,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:6",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَأَنتَ لَهُۥ تَصَدَّىٰ",
      "translation": "あなたは彼に掛かりきり。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "verse_number": 7,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:7",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَمَا عَلَيۡكَ أَلَّا يَزَّكَّىٰ",
      "translation": "彼が清められずとも、あなたには何のお咎めもないというのに。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "verse_number": 8,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:8",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَأَمَّا مَن جَآءَكَ يَسۡعَىٰ",
      "translation": "そして（あなたと会うことに）意気込んで、あなたのもとにやって来た者はといえば、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "verse_number": 9,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:9",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَهُوَ يَخۡشَىٰ",
      "translation": "（アッラー*を）恐れているというのに、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "verse_number": 10,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:10",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَأَنتَ عَنۡهُ تَلَهَّىٰ",
      "translation": "あなたは彼をそっちのけにしている。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "verse_number": 11,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:11",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "كَلَّآ إِنَّهَا تَذۡكِرَةٞ",
      "translation": "断じて（、使徒*よ、あなたがしたようなことは、許され）ない！実にそれ（このスーラ*）は、教訓なのだ。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "verse_number": 12,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:12",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَمَن شَآءَ ذَكَرَهُۥ",
      "translation": "そして誰でも（教訓を）望む者は、それ（啓示）を熟慮せよ。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "verse_number": 13,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:13",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فِي صُحُفٖ مُّكَرَّمَةٖ",
      "translation": "（このクルアーン*は）貴い書巻[1]の中、",
      "footnotes": "[1]　「貴い書巻」とは、守られし碑板*、あるいは啓典のこと（アル＝バガウィー５：21０参照）。"
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "verse_number": 14,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:14",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "مَّرۡفُوعَةٖ مُّطَهَّرَةِۭ",
      "translation": "（位）高く、（あらゆる不純さや改変から）清浄な（書巻の中）、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "verse_number": 15,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:15",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "بِأَيۡدِي سَفَرَةٖ",
      "translation": "使いの者（天使*）たちの手許にある。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "verse_number": 16,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:16",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "كِرَامِۭ بَرَرَةٖ",
      "translation": "高貴で、善良な者たちの（手許に）。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "verse_number": 17,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:17",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "قُتِلَ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ مَآ أَكۡفَرَهُۥ",
      "translation": "（不信仰な）人間が、成敗されますよう。彼は（自分の主*に対し）、何とひどい不信仰に陥っていることか！",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "verse_number": 18,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:18",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "مِنۡ أَيِّ شَيۡءٍ خَلَقَهُۥ",
      "translation": "かれ（アッラー*）は彼を、いかなるものからお創りになったのか？",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "verse_number": 19,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:19",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "مِن نُّطۡفَةٍ خَلَقَهُۥ فَقَدَّرَهُۥ",
      "translation": "一滴の精液から彼をお創りになり、それを（徐々に）調整されたのだ。[1]",
      "footnotes": "[1]　「その各身体器官、美醜（びしゅう）、大小、不幸な者となるか、幸福なものとなるか、ということなどをお決めになった」という解釈もある（アル＝クルトゥビー1９：21８参照）。尚、人間の創造の変遷（へんせん）については、巡礼*章５、信仰者たち章1４を参照。"
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "verse_number": 20,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:20",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ثُمَّ ٱلسَّبِيلَ يَسَّرَهُۥ",
      "translation": "それからかれ（アッラー*）は、道を容易くされ、[1]",
      "footnotes": "[1]　この「道」には、「母親の胎内から出て来ること」「真理と虚偽の道、及びその判別（人間章３とその訳注も参照）」「各自が運命づけられた物事」といった解釈がある（アル＝バガウィー５：211参照）。"
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "verse_number": 21,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:21",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ثُمَّ أَمَاتَهُۥ فَأَقۡبَرَهُۥ",
      "translation": "やがては彼に死を与えられ、墓にお埋めになり、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "verse_number": 22,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:22",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ثُمَّ إِذَا شَآءَ أَنشَرَهُۥ",
      "translation": "それから、かれがお望みになったら、（清算と報いのために、）彼を生き返させ給う。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "verse_number": 23,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:23",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "كَلَّا لَمَّا يَقۡضِ مَآ أَمَرَهُۥ",
      "translation": "断じて（、不信仰者*の状況は正しく）ない！彼は、かれ（アッラー*）が自分にご命じになったこと[1]を、遂行してはないないのだから。",
      "footnotes": "[1]　つまり信仰と、かれへの服従ということ（ムヤッサル５８５頁参照）。"
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "verse_number": 24,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:24",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَلۡيَنظُرِ ٱلۡإِنسَٰنُ إِلَىٰ طَعَامِهِۦٓ",
      "translation": "ならば人間に、自分の食べ物（が、いかに創造されたか）について考えさせてみよ。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "verse_number": 25,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:25",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَنَّا صَبَبۡنَا ٱلۡمَآءَ صَبّٗا",
      "translation": "われら*は、（地上に）水をざあざあと降らせ、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "verse_number": 26,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:26",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ثُمَّ شَقَقۡنَا ٱلۡأَرۡضَ شَقّٗا",
      "translation": "それから大地を、ひび割れさせ（、そこから各種の植物を芽出せさせ）たのだ。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "verse_number": 27,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:27",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَأَنۢبَتۡنَا فِيهَا حَبّٗا",
      "translation": "そして、われら*はそこに種粒を生育させた、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "verse_number": 28,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:28",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَعِنَبٗا وَقَضۡبٗا",
      "translation": "また、葡萄、まぐさ、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "verse_number": 29,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:29",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَزَيۡتُونٗا وَنَخۡلٗا",
      "translation": "オリーブ、ナツメヤシ、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "verse_number": 30,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:30",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَحَدَآئِقَ غُلۡبٗا",
      "translation": "木深い農園、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "verse_number": 31,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:31",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَفَٰكِهَةٗ وَأَبّٗا",
      "translation": "果実、牧草も（生育させた）、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "verse_number": 32,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:32",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "مَّتَٰعٗا لَّكُمۡ وَلِأَنۡعَٰمِكُمۡ",
      "translation": "あなた方と、あなた方の家畜の利益のために。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "verse_number": 33,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:33",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَإِذَا جَآءَتِ ٱلصَّآخَّةُ",
      "translation": "そして、（復活の日*を知らせる）轟きの一声[1]が到来した時（、人々は自分の事で、掛かりきりになる）。",
      "footnotes": "[1]　「轟きの一声」は、一説に、角笛が吹き鳴らされること（アル＝バイダーウィー５：４５４参照）。家畜章７３とその訳注も参照。"
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "verse_number": 34,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:34",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يَوۡمَ يَفِرُّ ٱلۡمَرۡءُ مِنۡ أَخِيهِ",
      "translation": "人間が、（その恐怖ゆえに、）自分の兄弟から逃げ出す日、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "verse_number": 35,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:35",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَأُمِّهِۦ وَأَبِيهِ",
      "translation": "また、自分の母親、父親、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "verse_number": 36,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:36",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَصَٰحِبَتِهِۦ وَبَنِيهِ",
      "translation": "自分の妻、子供たち（から逃げ出す日）。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "verse_number": 37,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:37",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لِكُلِّ ٱمۡرِيٕٖ مِّنۡهُمۡ يَوۡمَئِذٖ شَأۡنٞ يُغۡنِيهِ",
      "translation": "彼ら全員にはその日、自分のことだけで精一杯な用事がある。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "verse_number": 38,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:38",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ مُّسۡفِرَةٞ",
      "translation": "その日、（天国に入る）顔の数々は輝いており、",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "verse_number": 39,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:39",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ضَاحِكَةٞ مُّسۡتَبۡشِرَةٞ",
      "translation": "笑い、心躍らせている。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 40,
      "verse_number": 40,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:40",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَوُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَلَيۡهَا غَبَرَةٞ",
      "translation": "またその日、（地獄に入る）顔の数々は、その上に煤がかか（って真っ黒にな）る。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
      "verse_number": 41,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:41",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "تَرۡهَقُهَا قَتَرَةٌ",
      "translation": "埃がそれらを覆（い、辱めにあ）う。",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 42,
      "verse_number": 42,
      "page_number": 585,
      "verse_key": "80:42",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 234,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أُوْلَٰٓئِكَ هُمُ ٱلۡكَفَرَةُ ٱلۡفَجَرَةُ",
      "translation": "それらの者たちこそは、不信仰者*、放逸な者たちである。",
      "footnotes": ""
    }
  ]
}